                            </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Mean number of point mutations per sequence m" data-placement="top">Mutations per seq.</span>
